‪Oh, hindi.

05:00:15.250 --> 05:00:17.544
‪Hindi pwedeng ilagay ang karne
‪kapag maligamgam pa ang ihawan.

05:00:17.627 --> 05:00:19.838
‪Oo, kung hindi,
‪hindi masarap, maghintay ka.

05:00:22.799 --> 05:00:25.177
