‪Bakit biglaan?

05:00:34.686 --> 05:00:37.481
‪Sa totoo lang, simula pa lang,
‪nagtataka na rin ako.

05:00:39.816 --> 05:00:41.443
‪Hindi...

05:00:41.526 --> 05:00:43.487
‪Sa madaling salita...

05:00:45.989 --> 05:00:48.533
‪Nagkaroon ako ng spinal cancer noong walong taong gulang ako.

05:00:49.701 --> 05:00:52.037
‪Gumaling ako sa sakit noong sampung taong gulang,

05:00:53.622 --> 05:00:56.500
‪pero namatay ang
‪tatay ko.

05:00:58.043 --> 05:01:00.128
