05:01:04.299 --> 05:01:06.510
‪Pero sobrang gutom ako,

05:01:07.052 --> 05:01:08.261
‪kaya kinain ko nang palihim
‪ang mga tira-tirang jjajangmyeon

05:01:08.345 --> 05:01:10.722
